ular workshops at major conferences; and\nestablishing institutions and systems to support release practices that would\notherwise be onerous and error-prone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jul 2019 18:51:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2019 02:01:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-30"}
